data.description: Experience the Epitome of Luxury, Lifestyle, and Location! This highly sought-after Avery floor plan, boasting a spacious 2600+ square feet of customized living space, stands as a testament to Toll Brothers' early semi-custom designs in the coveted community of The Isles at Lakewood Ranch. Nestled on a serene homesite with a picturesque pond view, the southwest orientation offers unending visual delights, especially when the sunsets paint the sky with splendor.    The Avery floor plan effortlessly harmonizes living and sleeping areas, featuring en suite bedrooms for optimal comfort. The gourmet kitchen is a true masterpiece, adorned with elegant quartz countertops, a gas cook-top, convection wall oven-microwave combination, stylish stacked cabinets with under-cabinet lighting, a built-in JennAir stainless steel refrigerator, and a spacious walk-in pantry. Enjoy an immersive audio experience with surround sound speakers in the great room and strategically placed speakers in the garage. The garage is thoughtfully insulated and boasts over 20 recessed can lights.    Should your desires lean towards aquatic relaxation, ample space within the rear setbacks allows for the addition of a luxurious swimming pool or spa. Noteworthy features include a 22kW Gas-powered Generator with whole-house capability, ceiling fans in the garage, insulated garage attic, inside HVAC unit, instant hot water plumbing, exterior hose bibs thoughtfully placed on all four sides of the home, a motorized sunshade on the lanai, a video doorbell for enhanced security, a built-in vacuum system, a surge protector integrated into the electrical system breaker box, and so much more. Every detail in this Toll Brothers' Avery home exudes excellence.    The Isles at Lakewood Ranch is a desirable, private, and gated community that offers maintenance-included living, home security monitoring, and a rich array of amenities. Revel in the clubhouse, fitness room, Yoga/Pilates studio, pool, cabana, and the serenity of the nature boardwalk. This idyllic community is perfectly situated in the tranquil East corridor of Lakewood Ranch, just 10 minutes away from the vibrant shopping and dining destinations at Waterside Place, the Polo grounds, UTC shopping center, and the charm of downtown Main Street. Welcome to the pinnacle of Luxury Lifestyle living! (Buyer to verify interior measurements)
